des:
Bestpresso is an independent coffee brand bringing the highest quality coffee to your favorite machines. You can use this skill to search for your favorite products, manage your subscription, and hear about our policies. 

Here's how you can open this skill 
"Alexa, open bestpresso". 

Once inside the skill you can ask 
- Find k cups
- What's your return policy
